name: 20170101 - Embracer - 3D Neverending Story - CEGB Chord @ 100 bpm - NI Guitar Rig 5 - Discuss This Later.wav
description: This is one of the 38 different pad chord sample sounds from the memorable Embracer VST instrument which was included with an older version of Cubase, but which does not work anymore with the latest & greatest version Cubase 9... I think this is a pity. As a kind of honour to this little beauty I recorderd the CEGB chord at 100 bpm 4/4 for the 3D Neverending Story preset and then processed the sound using NI Guitar Rig 5 plugin. Created within Cubase 7.5. Mastering was done using Izotope Ozone 7.
